<br>
Could Iraq and its war machine ever threaten our borders as did Germany? I dont think so. If Germany were to have taken over Europe and the Soviet Union they would be free to mount their war effort against us, which they did want to do. What could Iraq do then? Terrorism. Terrorism presents a danger to our freedom, not from the people it kills, which on the whole is a very small percentage, but from the mentality that it breeds. Already, after sept 11th, the government under the leadership of GW and while waving a flag of so called &quot;patriotism&quot; has passed some very startling legislation that is very close to infringing on the freedoms that we as americans hold dear. And whats worse is that the general populace thinks its a good idea!! Case in point: the recent pole that says that people think the freedom of speech goes to far. <br>
